{"tid":380496,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高登創辦人DrJim：本地 IT 業有得做！","createTime":"2017-08-30T07:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T05:26:54.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff806df21bee206a2f1c0dcbe268cbcaf9526323","tid":380496,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T07:17:34.000Z","msg":"【e-zone 專訊】由《e-zone》舉辦，每年一度的「IT 傑出人士」選擇，今年由中國建設銀行（亞洲）信息技術管理部主管兼總經理王國良（圖）獲得，他的另一個身份是「DrJim」，也就是在 17 年前高登討論區網站的創辦人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1880000/1884688/cover_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1880000%2F1884688%2Fcover_1024.jpg&h=4b9730b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1884688\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1884688&d=hOj2yrHBh8ifRT3WMHuv3AtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=7c03128c\" target=\"_blank\">http://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1884688</a></div>"},{"pid":"d8829ecdf4f76d3379c8f75f717917934e80ea95","tid":380496,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T07:18:11.000Z","msg":"王國良認為，發展科技應該著眼於改善人民生活模式，而談及本地科技界的發展，這位高登「花打」指出香港人性格比較保守與官僚，以至政府部門在政策與牌照評估，每每用上半年或更久，令科技應用追不上進度。另一方面，香港普及 IT 教育不足，普遍中小學生都沒有 coding 或基本硬件知識，而與科技相關項目在大學選科時不屬學生最佳的選擇，往往令本地 IT 人才出現斷層。他概嘆本地科技從業員的形象低落，更有統計指出，他們對外印象只比建築工人稍高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"73fa459217277826de5eadd2384b168838549c47","tid":380496,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T07:18:46.000Z","msg":"近年銀行業難以找到合適人才，而且員工流失率嚴重，王國良透露自家公司亦是「受害者」之一，曾有競爭對手出動高 3 成人工「搶人」。他表示科技工種其實很廣泛，在銀行內非 IT 技術的職位也很多，系統顧問亦不是純工程師，但這方面的人才也十分缺乏。"},{"pid":"263e802a032c1883b9c733fd5277994c444790ed","tid":380496,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T07:19:08.000Z","msg":"IT 入行的門檻不高，很多出色員工大學本科非科技或工程出身，王國良寄語IT 人必須有「解決問題」的熱誠，更要有較高的溝通能力，以連接客戶與應用設計的需求，他們更要具備行業通識，與基礎技術知識。隨著未來人工智能（AI）興起，他相信 IT 人發展機會十分多，特別是香港市場的集資能力強勁，FinTech 科技成長可期，故此十分鼓勵更多新人，甚至是新一代投入行業。<br />\n<br />\n本年度「IT 傑出人士」其餘兩位得獎人士，尚包括客路（Klook Travel）聯合創辦人王志豪， Tink Labs Limited 創辦人郭頌賢。"},{"pid":"37c17123470bd42fa90a2c7e94ff407f85db59fc","tid":380496,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T07:24:03.000Z","msg":"@老貓再世_"},{"pid":"dc118ae715e8841ba7cfb1e0554ddeeac050e47c","tid":380496,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T07:24:16.000Z","msg":"入IT 仲要入銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67875275b30aafc7831bc7730976c15701e2b9af","tid":380496,"uid":1096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T07:26:31.000Z","msg":"王國良透露自家公司亦是「受害者」之一，曾有競爭對手出動高 3 成人工「搶人」。<br />\n<br />\n多3成咁少學人搶人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d672e0c68190f6270b0bc4431bb032619c8ef9","tid":380496,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T07:27:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"919f97f150adce12dafd8fc5a71ba67c1a74d30e","tid":380496,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T07:35:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/144734_b5ac2839b3c28d411abc6096c4b40e84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F15%2F144734_b5ac2839b3c28d411abc6096c4b40e84.jpg&h=d50ca8cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e62e676057714b8fcd87c24551e097b3964c44d3","tid":380496,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c